criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  reside in Milwaukee county;

          -  are at least 18 years of age;

          -  self-identify as male;

          -  self-identify as Black or African-American;

          -  can provide informed consent;

          -  report unprotected anal sex with a man in the past 3 months;

          -  report at least two sexual partners with whom they have had unprotected anal or
             vaginal sex in the past 3 months;

          -  are willing to be tested for HIV using rapid oral fluid procedures or willing to
             provide evidence of HIV seropositivity

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Under 18 years of age,

          -  involvement in a HIV prevention study currently or in the past 6 months,

          -  Participation in the pilot phase
